.TH hsh 1 "6 January 2025" "1.0" "hsh"
.SH NAME
hsh - basic shell that can execute commands, handle arguments from the command line 
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ./hsh
.B to enter interactive mode 

.SS Interactive mode
[command [argument...]]

example: 
oem@Mao-Yoga:~/holbertonschool-simple_shell$ ./hsh                                                                                                                       
simple_shell$ ls -l                                                                                                                                                      
